{"tid":823774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東鐵綫有限度服務　沙田站至大埔墟站每22分鐘一班","createTime":"2018-09-17T00:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T01:00:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c426c284b8bcef6139ff467ad10a7872d92660","tid":823774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1418424_2_L_20180917085318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1418424_2_L_20180917085318.jpg&h=1b565312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山竹吹襲本港後，海陸空交通受阻。九巴、龍運巴士，新巴及城巴，除部分路線外，所有日間路線暫停服務，至於新大嶼山巴士就有部分巴士線陸續恢復服務。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵方面，東鐵綫及輕鐵提供有限度服務。其中紅磡站至沙田站每10分鐘一班，沙田站至大埔墟站每22分鐘一班，上水至落馬洲每15分鐘一班，上水至羅湖每10分鐘一班，大埔墟站至上水站暫停服務，荃灣錢及觀塘綫就每8分鐘一班。<br />\n<br />\n另外，天星小輪的中環至尖沙咀及灣仔至尖沙咀航綫，早上恢復服務。<br />\n<br />\n機場今天起就會實施航班重新編配，預計今日早上6時至午夜12時，可處理897班來往香港的航班，兩條跑道晚上會通宵運作，以疏導受影響的旅客。"},{"pid":"7c95ff6c26db21e8ca99441643a1a20c106ffc75","tid":823774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418424-20180917.htm#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418424-20180917.htm%23&d=jswbPQnabvIpAkxVJWlMCwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=992ae751\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418424-20180917.htm%23&h=d518ae9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418424-20180917.htm#</a>"},{"pid":"6573e1bffc3676e0a54afbb23ca10abbddee73dc","tid":823774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}